#: ../../user/plotting.rst:3
msgid "Plotting Results"
msgstr "繪製結果"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:5
msgid ""
"Spinning Up ships with a simple plotting utility for interpreting "
"results. Run it with:"
msgstr "Spinning Up 附帶了一個簡單的繪圖工具用於解讀結果。使用以下命令執行："

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:14
msgid "**Positional Arguments:**"
msgstr "**位置引數：**"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:18
msgid ""
"*strings*. As many log directories (or prefixes to log directories, which"
" the plotter will autocomplete internally) as you'd like to plot from. "
"Logdirs will be searched recursively for experiment outputs."
msgstr ""
"*strings*。你想要繪製的任意數量的日誌目錄"
"（或日誌目錄的前綴，繪圖工具會在內部自動補全）。"
"系統會遞迴搜尋日誌目錄以尋找實驗輸出。"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:20
msgid "You Should Know"
msgstr "你應該知道"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:22
msgid ""
"The internal autocompleting is really handy! Suppose you have run several"
" experiments, with the aim of comparing performance between different "
"algorithms, resulting in a log directory structure of:"
msgstr ""
"內部自動補全功能非常方便！假設你已經執行了幾個實驗，"
"目的是比較不同演算法之間的效能，產生了如下的日誌目錄結構："

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:34
msgid "You can easily produce a graph comparing algo1 and algo2 with:"
msgstr "你可以輕鬆地使用以下命令產生比較 algo1 和 algo2 的圖表："

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:40
msgid ""
"relying on the autocomplete to find both ``data/bench_algo1`` and "
"``data/bench_algo2``."
msgstr ""
"利用自動補全功能來找到 ``data/bench_algo1`` 和 ``data/bench_algo2``。"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:42
msgid "**Optional Arguments:**"
msgstr "**可選引數：**"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:46
msgid ""
"*strings*. Optional way to specify legend for the plot. The plotter "
"legend will automatically use the ``exp_name`` from the ``config.json`` "
"file, unless you tell it otherwise through this flag. This only works if "
"you provide a name for each directory that will get plotted. (Note: this "
"may not be the same as the number of logdir args you provide! Recall that"
" the plotter looks for autocompletes of the logdir args: there may be "
"more than one match for a given logdir prefix, and you will need to "
"provide a legend string for each one of those matches---unless you have "
"removed some of them as candidates via selection or exclusion rules "
"(below).)"
msgstr ""
"*strings*。指定圖表圖例的可選方式。"
"繪圖工具的圖例會自動使用 ``config.json`` 檔案中的 ``exp_name``，除非你透過此旗標另行指定。"
"此功能僅在你為每個要繪製的目錄提供名稱時才有效。"
"（注意：這可能與你提供的日誌目錄引數數量不同！"
"請記住繪圖工具會自動補全日誌目錄引數：一個日誌目錄前綴可能有多個匹配項，"
"你需要為每個匹配項提供一個圖例字串——除非你已透過選擇或排除規則（見下文）移除了部分候選項。）"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:50
msgid "*string*. Pick what column from data is used for the x-axis."
msgstr "*string*。選擇資料中的哪一欄用作 x 軸。"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:54
msgid ""
"*strings*. Pick what columns from data to graph on the y-axis. Submitting"
" multiple values will produce multiple graphs. Defaults to "
"``Performance``, which is not an actual output of any algorithm. Instead,"
" ``Performance`` refers to either ``AverageEpRet``, the correct "
"performance measure for the on-policy algorithms, or "
"``AverageTestEpRet``, the correct performance measure for the off-policy "
"algorithms. The plotter will automatically figure out which of "
"``AverageEpRet`` or ``AverageTestEpRet`` to report for each separate "
"logdir."
msgstr ""
"*strings*。選擇資料中的哪些欄位繪製在 y 軸上。提供多個值會產生多個圖表。"
"預設為 ``Performance``，這不是任何演算法的實際輸出。"
"``Performance`` 實際上指的是 ``AverageEpRet``（同策略演算法的正確效能指標）"
"或 ``AverageTestEpRet``（離策略演算法的正確效能指標）。"
"繪圖工具會自動判斷每個日誌目錄應報告 ``AverageEpRet`` 還是 ``AverageTestEpRet``。"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:58
msgid ""
"Optional flag. By default, the plotter shows y-values which are averaged "
"across all results that share an ``exp_name``, which is typically a set "
"of identical experiments that only vary in random seed. But if you'd like"
" to see all of those curves separately, use the ``--count`` flag."
msgstr ""
"可選旗標。預設情況下，繪圖工具顯示的 y 值是所有共享相同 ``exp_name`` 的結果的平均值，"
"這通常是一組僅隨機種子不同的相同實驗。"
"如果你想分別查看所有這些曲線，請使用 ``--count`` 旗標。"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:62
msgid ""
"*int*. Smooth data by averaging it over a fixed window. This parameter "
"says how wide the averaging window will be."
msgstr "*int*。透過固定窗口平均來平滑資料。此參數指定平均窗口的寬度。"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:66
msgid ""
"*strings*. Optional selection rule: the plotter will only show curves "
"from logdirs that contain all of these substrings."
msgstr ""
"*strings*。可選的篩選規則：繪圖工具只會顯示日誌目錄包含所有這些子字串的曲線。"

#: ../../user/plotting.rst:70
msgid ""
"*strings*. Optional exclusion rule: plotter will only show curves from "
"logdirs that do not contain these substrings."
msgstr ""
"*strings*。可選的排除規則：繪圖工具只會顯示日誌目錄不包含這些子字串的曲線。"
